<div class="col-md-12 sweeps-rules" style="padding-top: 25px; margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #dddddd">  
<h3 style="color: #4d4d4d"><strong>Value City Furniture &amp; American Signature Furniture Labor Day Sweepstakes</strong></h3>  
<h4 style="color: #4d4d4d"> <strong>OFFICIAL RULES</strong></h4>          
<p class="text-uppercase">        NO PURCHASE OR PAYMENT OF ANY KIND IS NECESSARY TO ENTER FOR A CHANCE TO WIN. BY PARTICIPATING IN THE CONTEST, ENTRANT AGREES TO BE BOUND BY THESE OFFICIAL RULES.           </p>          
<p><br />
Sponsored by American Signature, Inc.</p>          
<p>            <br />
        The Value City Furniture & American Signature Furniture Labor Day Sweepstakes ("Contest") encourages visitors to go to the website of Value City Furniture ("VCF") or American Signature Furniture ("ASF")  to add items to an online shopping cart and be automatically entered into a drawing] for a chance to win a prize. The selection of a winner will be chosen in the sole discretion of American Signature, Inc. ("Sponsor"). <br />
          </p>          
<p>            <br />
        <strong>1. TIMING: </strong>The entry period begins at approximately 12:00 p.m. EST on August 9, 2016 and ends at approximately 11:59 p.m. EST on August 30, 2016 ("Entry Period").           </p>          
<p>            <br />
        <strong>2. ELIGIBILITY: </strong>The person entering the Contest ("Entrant") must be 18 years of age or older at the time of entry. The Contest is open to any U.S. citizen that is a resident of the United States (and its territories and possessions) who, as of August 9, 2016, is at least 18 years of age and lives in either the VCF or ASF market area. All other Entrants will be disqualified. Entrants are not eligible to win a prize through both VCF and ASF. All entrants are only eligible to win one prize from either VCF or ASF one time per calendar year. Employees of Sponsor and its divisions, subsidiaries or affiliates, their immediate families and/or household members are not eligible to participate.            </p>          
<p>            <br />
        <strong>3. CONDITIONS OF PARTICIPATION:</strong> : Entering the Contest by submitting an Entry (as defined below) constitutes Entrant's agreement to abide by and be bound by these Official Rules. Being eligible to win the Contest is contingent upon the fulfillment of all requirements set forth in these Official Rules. Decisions of Sponsor are final and binding in all matters related to entry and the winner's selection process (as defined in these Official Rules).             </p>          
<p>            <br />
        <strong>4. TO ENTER:</strong> During the Entry Period, Entrant must go to the website of VCF (HTTP://WWW.VALUECITYFURNITURE.COM) or ASF (HTTP://WWW.AMERICANSIGNATUREFURNITURE.COM) and create an account or use an existing account to add items to your online shopping cart  for a chance to win a $500 VCF or ASF gift card ("Entry"). Entrant must be the person who is the authorized owner or domain name owner of the email address associated with the Entry. Entrants are not eligible to win more than once and only one Entry is permitted per person.            </p>          
<p>            <br />
        <strong>5. SELECTION OF WINNERS:</strong> Winners will be chosen at random by Sponsor during three separate drawings as described below.  Winners chosen by Sponsor are final pending confirmation of eligibility in accordance with these Official Rules. Winner selection for a $500 VCF or ASF gift card will take place on or about August 16, August 23, and August 30, 2016.  Winners will be announced within 72 hours of each drawing.  Winnerâ€™s zip code will determine brand of $500 gift card.  All Entries have the same chances of winning based on the total number of eligible Entries received.  Each Entry is eligible for the weekly drawing during the Entry Period.            </p>          
<p>            <br />
        <strong>6. PRIZES:</strong> Sponsor will choose at random one person per brand per drawing to win a VCF or ASF $500 gift card. Winning prizes are non-negotiable and non-transferable. Entrants will be notified via email or phone by Sponsor of their selection as a winner, along with instructions on how winner may claim the prize. If Sponsor does not receive a response from a winner within 48 hours of notification, Sponsor reserves the right to choose another winner or terminate prize.              </p>          
<p>            <br />
        <strong>7. LIMITATIONS OF LIABILITY AND RELEASE:</strong> By entering the Contest, Entrants agree to release and hold harmless Sponsor and its parent, officers, directors, employees and agencies (collectively, the "Released Parties") from and against any claim or cause of action arising out of or in connection with the Entrant's participation in the Contest. Entrants further agree that in any cause of action, the Released Parties' liability will be limited to the costs of entering and participating in the Contest and in no event shall the Released Parties be liable for attorney's fees. Entrants waive the right to claim any other additional damages whatsoever, including but not limited to, punitive, consequential, direct or indirect damages. By entering the Contest, Entrants agree to release and hold harmless the Released Parties from any and all liability for injuries, death or losses or damages to persons or property AS WELL AS CLAIMS/ACTIONS BASED ON COPYRIGHT OR INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY INFRINGEMENT, MISAPPROPRIATION, PUBLICITY RIGHTS, DEFAMATION AND/OR INVASION OF PRIVACY.           </p>          
<p>            <br />
        <strong>8. USE OF DATA:</strong> Sponsor may collect personal data about Entrants in accordance with its Privacy Policy. CLICK HERE to review the Privacy Policy. By entering the Contest, Entrants acknowledge and agree to Sponsor's collection and usage of their personal information and acknowledge that they have read and accepted Sponsor's Privacy Policy.           </p>          
<p>            <br />
          <strong>9. WINNERS' LIST REQUEST:</strong> To request confirmation of the name and address of the winners of the Contest, please send a self-addressed, stamped business size envelope, by September 15, 2016 to: VCF/ASF Labor Day Sweepstakes, American Signature Inc. Marketing Department, 4300 Fifth Avenue, Columbus, Ohio 43219.           </p>   </div></div></div>
